  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\">You create a magical sickle erupting from the ground that swings at an opponent within range. On a failed save a creature takes 1d6 slashing damage and 1 persistent bleed damage. Casting this spell with 2 actions targets a single creature within range, while casting this spell with 3 actions creates a 5-foot burst from a space within range.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Critical Success</strong> The creature takes no damage.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Success </strong>The creature takes the persistent bleed damage.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Failure</strong> The creature takes full slashing and persistent bleed damage.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double slashing and persistent bleed damage.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Heightened(+1) </strong>The initial damage increases by 1d6 and the persistent damage increases by 1.</p>"
